<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1675594-in-ch-2-at-the-still-point-the">In ch. 2 &quot;At the Still Point&quot; the characters mourn the death of their friend Jamie. In ch. 10 &quot;The Secrets of Summer&quot; we find out that Jamie is a vampire, and so is Dirk, who was with him when he died. Question: does this change anything about what we read in ch. 2? for example, is Jamie even dead? Is ch. 10 a flashback or the present?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1675594'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F9914.The_Informers">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1675594-in-ch-2-at-the-still-point-the">2 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1675594-in-ch-2-at-the-still-point-the">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

