</a><br><br>But what if he mixed that sort of tale with a little bit of . . . . . <br><br><a href="https://lunapic.com" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1603980899ra/30305429.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
