          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780330536325" href="/book/show/9722646-the-informers">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/25471005-sean-blake?shelf=short-stories">short-stories</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1036060454" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7275439449523931501">Ellis is a great writer when it comes to observing the bland superficiality of our modern society, savagely satirical depictions of capitalist America and its inhabitants.<br/><br/>One of my favourite short story collections from a master writer.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


